<h5 class="kt-adv-heading0df1d2-c6 wp-block-kadence-advancedheading" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading0df1d2-c6"><strong><mark style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)" class="has-inline-color has-theme-palette-10-color">Paulina Matysiak &ndash; pos&#322;anka na&nbsp;Sejm RP<br></mark></strong></h5></section><section id="block-49" class="widget widget_block"><style>.wp-block-kadence-advancedheading.kt-adv-heading99692c-4c, .wp-block-kadence-advancedheading.kt-adv-heading99692c-4c[data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading99692c-4c"]{font-style:normal;}.wp-block-kadence-advancedheading.kt-adv-heading99692c-4c mark.kt-highlight, .wp-block-kadence-advancedheading.kt-adv-heading99692c-4c[data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading99692c-4c"] mark.kt-highlight{font-style:normal;color:#f76a0c;-webkit-box-decoration-break:clone;box-decoration-break:clone;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;}.wp-block-kadence-advancedheading.kt-adv-heading99692c-4c img.kb-inline-image, .wp-block-kadence-advancedheading.kt-adv-heading99692c-4c[data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading99692c-4c"] img.kb-inline-image{width:150px;vertical-align:baseline;}</style>
<p class="kt-adv-heading99692c-4c wp-block-kadence-advancedheading" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading99692c-4c">Nazywam si&#281; Paulina Matysiak, pochodz&#281; z&nbsp;Kutna i&nbsp;od&nbsp;2019 roku pe&#322;ni&#281; mandat pos&#322;anki na&nbsp;Sejm RP. W&nbsp;2023 roku wyborcy ponownie powierzyli mi&nbsp;t&#281;&nbsp;funkcj&#281;.<br></p></section><section id="block-50" class="widget widget_block widget_text"><p>Reprezentuj&#281; powiaty kutnowski, &#322;aski, &#322;&#281;czycki, &#322;owicki, pabianicki, paj&#281;cza&#324;ski, podd&#281;bicki, sieradzki, wielu&#324;ski, wieruszowski, zdu&#324;skowolski i&nbsp;zgierski.</p></section>	</div>
</div><!-- .footer-widget3 -->
					</div>
